description: With the FIFA World Cup on, I knew it would be great to seduce and persuade some young football fans. So I took my cam and went to a big garden, where I knew they do public viewing. It was packed with German and Portuguese fans. It took some time till I´ve found some young Czech lads. Best things about football is, that no one is watching it by himself. I´ve joined two friends, one of them really reminded me that German player Schweinsteiger. I´ve been waiting for the right moment to start my sex-for-money negotiation. I´ve tried what didn´t work for a long time. Asked them to be a true friends and to go into this deal together. Trust me Gents, when I say that these two guy are true brothers and they do everything together.
title: Czech Hunter 147
